<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_52ddfd4a0f5c.aspx"><b>国风·鄘风·相鼠</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson52ddfd4a0f5c">
相鼠有皮，人而无仪！人而无仪，不死何为？<br />相鼠有齿，人而无止！人而无止，不死何俟？<br />相鼠有体，人而无礼，人而无礼！胡不遄死？
</div>
